org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwPhysical.HwLayout

Interface HwComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HwCoolingSupply, HwPowerSupply
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwComponentImpl, HwCoolingSupplyImpl, HwPowerSupplyImpl

    public interface HwComponent
extends HwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Kind
    • Dimensions
    • Area
    • Position
    • Grid
    • Nb Pins
    • Weight
    • Price
    • RConditions
    • Powered Services
    • Static Consumption
    • Static Dissipation
    • Sub Components
    See Also:
    HwLayoutPackage.getHwComponent()
